name: Fellowes Powershred 225Ci 100% Jam Proof Cross-Cut Shredder FEL3825001

reviews.name: Fellowes C-225Ci Jam Proof Commercial Shredder
reviews.reviewText: I had this shreadder for a couple of weeks, and so far, I am pleased with its performance. It is not overly noisy and does the job. I bought it from Walmart on line, at the lowest price in comparison to others, and a couple of day later I picked it up at my local store. But I ran out of plastic bags, a few are provided with the machine, and I needed them right away, so I went to several office supplys stores, even Home Depot, but could not find a 16 gallons bag size. Then, I went to Smart and Final, they sell a 16 to 20 gallons plastic bag size, and it fits perfect.
reviews.title: Good choice
